# VALUE changelog

Package VALUE is the continuation of the former package [R.VALUE](https://github.com/SantanderMetGroup/R_VALUE). See its history in <https://github.com/SantanderMetGroup/R_VALUE/releases>

## v2.0.0
 * `loadValueStations` has been deprecated, and will be eventually removed in future pakage versions. The user is now referred to `loadStationData` from package `loadeR`
 * New atomic function `valueIndex1D`, for index calculation on time series vectors
 * New functions `show.indices` and `show.diagnostics`, providing a list of available indices/diagnostics 






